If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : tvshopfusion@gmail.com

You can simply ask Alexa to clean up, cleaning finished. There’s no need to go to the switch to start you cleaner - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.

After connecting Alexa to your Orage products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Orage" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Orage account in our "Orage" app;
(3). You need to have some Orage devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Orage" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Orage" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Orage" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Orage", and you'll be navigated to Orage login page;
(9). Input your Orage account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on vacuum"
“Alexa, turn off vacuum"
